Conventional
```python
numbers = [1,2,3,4,5,6,7,8]

even_number = []
for num in numbers:
	if num%2 == 0:
		even_number.append(num)
```

List comprehension
```python
numbers = [1,2,3,4,5,6,7,8]
even_number = [num for num in numbers if num%2 == 0]
```
